<!DOCTYPE html><html><head><meta charset="utf-8" /><meta content="IE=edge,chrome=1" http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" /><title>Rack - Prosty parser haml</title><link href="http://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Droid+Sans:400,700|Bitter:400,700,400italic|Open+Sans:300italic,400italic,700italic,400,300,700" media="screen" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" /><link href="../assets/stylesheets/all-f5ec2720.css" media="screen" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" /><script src="../assets/javascripts/all-eca7008a.js" type="text/javascript"></script></head><body class="x2009 x2009_rack-prosty-parser-haml"><div class="navbar navbar-default"><div class="navbar-collapse collapse navbar-responsive-collapse"><div class="container"><ul class="nav navbar-nav"><li><a class="navbar-brand" href="/">Blog</a></li><li><a class="navbar-brand" href="/about.html">About</a></li><li><a class="navbar-brand" href="/projects.html">Projects</a></li><li><a class="navbar-brand" href="/talks.html">Talks</a></li></ul></div></div></div><div class="container"><article class="post"><div class="page-header"><div class="row"><div class="col-md-10"><h1>Rack - Prosty parser haml</h1></div><div class="col-md-2 post-date"><time datetime="2009-01-05">Jan  5, 2009</time></div></div></div><div class="alert alert-info">This article is written in Polish and was originally
<a href="http://teamon.jogger.pl/2009/01/05/rack-prosty-parser-haml">published at Jogger</a>.</div><div class="lead"><p>Jakiś czas temu stwierdziłem, że przydała by mi się aplikacja do parsowania plików <a href="http://haml.hamptoncatlin.com">haml</a> podczas tworzenia designu dla strony. Z pomocą przyszedł <a href="http://rack.rubyforge.org">rack</a>.</p>

<p>Wszystko zakończyło się w 13 linijkach ;)</p>
<pre class="highlight ruby"><span class="nb">require</span> <span class="s2">"rack/response"</span>
<span class="nb">require</span> <span class="s2">"haml"</span>

<span class="n">app</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="no">Proc</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nf">new</span> <span class="k">do</span> <span class="o">|</span><span class="n">env</span><span class="o">|</span>
  <span class="n">path</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">env</span><span class="o">[</span><span class="s2">"REQUEST_URI"</span><span class="o">]</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nf">sub</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s2">"/"</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="s2">""</span><span class="p">)</span>
  <span class="k">if</span> <span class="n">path</span> <span class="o">=~</span> <span class="sr">/\.haml$/</span>
    <span class="o">[</span><span class="mi">200</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="p">{</span><span class="s2">"Content-type"</span> <span class="o">=&gt;</span> <span class="s2">"text/html"</span><span class="p">},</span> <span class="no">Haml</span><span class="o">::</span><span class="no">Engine</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nf">new</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="no">File</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nf">read</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">path</span><span class="p">)).</span><span class="nf">render</span><span class="o">]</span>
  <span class="k">else</span>
    <span class="no">Rack</span><span class="o">::</span><span class="no">File</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nf">new</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="no">Dir</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nf">pwd</span><span class="p">).</span><span class="nf">call</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">env</span><span class="p">)</span>
  <span class="k">end</span>
<span class="k">end</span>

<span class="n">run</span> <span class="n">app</span>
</pre>
<p>A wszystko odpalane poprzez:</p>
<pre class="highlight shell">thin start -R design.ru -p 9999
</pre>
<p>W przeglądarce wpisujemy np. &ldquo;localhost:9999/foo/bar.haml&rdquo; i zostanie wyrenderowany plik <code>bar.haml</code> z folderu <code>foo</code>. Pliki inne niż <code>.haml</code> nie zostaną zparsowane.</p>
